Interface Parsable<T>

    public interface Parsable<T>

      • parse

        ParseResult<T> parse(String input)
        Tries to parse the input and returns a ParseResult object. This should never return null as parse errors will be indicated in the returned object.
        Parameters:
        input - To parse
        Returns:
        The output result of the operation
